<h4 class="wp-block-heading">Lower Two</h4>



<p>Lower body day two continues to work on your legs, concentrating on different muscle groups. Exercises like leg presses and calf raises provide variety and help prevent overuse injuries. This day further develops leg strength, promotes muscle balance, and supports functional movements like walking, running, and climbing stairs.</p>



